posts.text:
Kela: Tuttu taksinkuljettaja on monelle tärkeä - korvauksia maksettiin 2,8 miljoonasta taksimatkasta Karjalainen 
Tuoreen tutkimuksen mukaan osaa matkustajista huolettaa sairausvakuutuksen korvaamilla taksimatkoilla taksin tilaaminen ja saapuminen sekä avun saaminen. Taksimatkat vaikuttivat kuitenkin toteutuneen pääosin hyvin, Kela tiedottaa. 
Taksitilaukset hoidetaan nykyään keskitetysti sairaanhoitopiirikohtaisista tilausnumeroista. Se mahdollistaa taksikuljetusten yhdistelyn, mikä tuo säästöjä korvausmenoihin. 
Kelan mukaan matkustajat pitivät kuljetusten yhdistelyä järkevänä ja jopa ehdottivat nykyistä tehokkaampaa yhdistelyä. 
Yhdistely kuitenkin pidentää matka-aikoja. Pitkät tai usein tehtävät matkat koettiin raskaiksi jo ennen yhdistelyä. Lisäksi vastaajat olivat huolissaan siitä, johtaako se myöhästymiseen tai matkanteon hankaloitumiseen. Moni kaipasi myös tuttua taksinkuljettajaa. 
– Tuttu kuljettaja vahvistaa luottamusta ja turvallisuuden tunnetta. Hän huolehtii matkan sujumisesta ja tietää, miten matkustajaa pitää auttaa. Silloin esimerkiksi omaishoitajan ei välttämättä tarvitse lähteä matkalle mukaan, tutkija Päivi Tillman Kelasta sanoo. 
Oikeuden vakiotaksinkäyttöön voi edelleen saada terveydentilan ja yksilökohtaisen tarveharkinnan perusteella. Oikeus on tällä hetkellä runsaalla 10 000 henkilöllä. 
Kelan mukaan matkakorvausjärjestelmään itsessään matkustajat olivat tyytyväisiä. Omavastuuta ja etenkin alkuvuoden maksurasitusta ennen vuotuisen maksukaton täyttymistä he pitivät kuitenkin korkeana. 
– Matkustajien mielipiteitä ja kokemuksia matkoista ja korvauksista olisi hyödyllistä seurata jatkossakin esimerkiksi vuosittaisella haastattelututkimuksella, Tillman kertoo. 
Helsingin yliopiston ja Kelan tutkimuksessa haastateltiin sairausvakuutuksen matkakorvausten käyttäjiä matkojen toteutumisesta, matkakorvausten hausta ja merkityksestä sekä matkalla tarvittavasta avusta. 
Useimmat korvauksen saajat matkustivat hoitoon tai kuntoutukseen viikoittain. Useimmat korvauksen saajat tarvitsivat apuvälineitä liikkumiseensa. 
Haastatteluja tehtäessä taksimatkojen tilausten keskittämisestä oli kulunut alueesta riippuen korkeintaan 4 vuotta. Joillakin alueilla muutos oli vasta tulossa. 
Vuonna 2016 Kela maksoi matkakorvauksia taksimatkoista yli 300 000 henkilölle. Kaikkiaan korvauksia maksettiin 2,8 miljoonasta taksimatkasta, Kela ilmoittaa.

posts.title: Considerations To Make When Hiring A Professional In Termite Removal Blue Island
posts.text:
By Eric Watson 

Sometimes it becomes hard for a homeowner to control pests and therefore there is the need to hire a professional for the job. When there is a termite infestation, the products to use to clear them are often for certified professionals. Therefore, an expert pest controller is a must hire in this case. In this article, the weight will be on the factors that one should consider when hiring a professional in termite removal Blue Island .

First, ensure that the person you are hiring knows the available pest control measures. The person should answer any question you ask him about pests and also know how to control them. If the individual has no idea of what you are requesting, he should be honest and say so instead of claiming to have expertise. In such a situation, go ahead and look for other professionals who have qualifications to understand the industry.

The professional appearance of the expert is worth checking, and one should consider this as an act of professionalism. The person should have an overall professional look with regards to cleanliness and the also the equipment he uses. One should hire someone who is professionally presentable.

Ask around for references to get the best service provider in the market. One can approach friends or neighbors and ask them if they have an idea of someone who can help in controlling pests. Also, one can use other means such as online search to look for the right professionals. The local pest associations can also be an excellent avenue to make progress when looking for a pest control expert.

Ensure that the profession gives you a quotation of all the services he offers. As much as you may want the price to be affordable to you, it is better that you go for quality instead of price. The cost of the services should be considerate but also be commensurate with the services given. One should avoid low rates because they may imply that the services offered will be below standards.

It is vital that the expert gives you a contract. One should discuss the options that are available for the current problem. Ensure that the professional has convinced you on how to tackle the whole problem for good. He should give you timelines on when to carry out the task and give you a maintenance schedule. Understand all the details in the contract before you sign it.

The pest control specialist should give you the details of all the chemicals he will use for the process. Make sure that all the questions that you have regarding the substances get satisfactory answers. As expected, most compounds in these chemicals will have a side effect, and therefore the professional should give you solutions on what you need to use in case the chemical overreacts.

Lastly, the professional should be willing to give you a guarantee of the services he is offering you. The expert should be ready to stand by his work and the results. Let the warranty be in writing.

posts.author: Alexandros G. Sfakianakis,Anapafseos 5 Agios Nikolaos 72100 Crete Greece,00306932607174,00302841026182 (noreply@blogger.com)
posts.title: Invited review: Breeding and ethical perspectives on genetically modified and genome edited cattle
posts.text:
Publication date: Available online 6 November 2017
Source: Journal of Dairy Science
Author(s): S. Eriksson, E. Jonas, L. Rydhmer, H. Röcklinsberg
The hot topic of genetic modification and genome editing is sometimes presented as a rapid solution to various problems in the field of animal breeding and genetics. These technologies hold potential for future use in agriculture but we need to be aware of difficulties in large-scale application and integration in breeding schemes. In this review, we discuss applications of both classical genetic modifications (GM) using vectors and genome editing in dairy cattle breeding. We use an interdisciplinary approach considering both ethical and animal breeding perspectives. Decisions on how to make use of these techniques need to be made based not only on what is possible, but on what is reasonable to do. Principles of animal integrity, naturalness, risk perception, and animal welfare issues are examples of ethically relevant factors to consider. These factors also influence public perception and decisions about regulations by authorities. We need to acknowledge that we lack complete understanding of the genetic background of complex traits. It may be difficult, therefore, to predict the full effect of certain modifications in large-scale breeding programs. We present 2 potential applications: genome editing to dispense with dehorning, and insertion of human genes in bovine genomes to improve udder health as an example of classical GM. Both of these cases could be seen as beneficial for animal welfare but they differ in other aspects. In the former case, a genetic variant already present within the species is introduced, whereas in the latter case, transgenic animals are generated—this difference may influence how society regards the applications. We underline that the use of GM, as well as genome editing, of farm animals such as cattle is not independent of the context, and should be considered as part of an entire process, including, for example, the assisted reproduction technology that needs to be used. We propose that breeding organizations and breeding companies should take an active role in ethical discussions about the use of these techniques and thereby signal to society that these questions are being responsibly addressed.

posts.text: نماینده مردم خوزستان در مجلس خبرگان: شور زائران اربعین مسئولیت مدیران برای خدمات رسانی را بیشتر می کند شناسهٔ خبر: 4137481 - استانها > خوزستان چذابه ـ نماینده مردم خوزستان در مجلس خبرگان گفت: شور و نشاط زائران اربعین، مسئولیت مدیران در ارائه خدمات بهتر به زائران و فراهم کردن زیرساخت های موجود در مرزها بیشتر می کند. آیت الله سیدعلی شفیعی در گفتگو با خبرنگار مهر مستقر در چذابه اظهار کرد: به دلیل تجاربی که از گذشته داشتیم، اثرگذاری مراسم اربعین در آینده بسیار امیدوارکننده خواهد بود. وی افزود: اثرگذاری قیام امام حسین (ع) در شور و حال عاشقان حسینی به وضوح مشاهده می شود و هر سال شاهد گسترش این شور حسینی هستیم. نماینده مردم خوزستان در مجلس خبرگان تصریح کرد: جوش و خروش و حماسه بین مردم است و آثار آنچه امروز می بینیم نیز در آینده متجلی می شود. شفیعی در ارتباط با پیام حرکت اربعین بیان کرد: نه تنها مردم ایران بلکه مردم دنیا پی به حقانیت اسلام و مذهب شیعه می برند و متوجه می شوند ارادتی که شیعیان به اهل بیت دارند انشاالله در دنیا و آخرت مؤثر خواهد بود. وی در پایان عنوان کرد: مراسم اربعین حسینی همه ساله با شکوه بیشتری برگزار و به تعداد زائران اضافه می شود، این شور مسئولیت تمامی مسئولان را در حوزه ارائه خدمات بهتر به زائران و فراهم کردن زیرساخت های موجود در مرزها بیشتر می کند. برچسب‌ها
